title: NYX Butter Gloss 3 Piece Set - Sweet Temptations - Apple Strudel, Eclair & Cherry Pie 0.27 fl oz. 8mL
description:
Be Prepared to captivate your lover's attention with our "Sweet Temptation" Butter Glosses set.   

Our Butter Glosses have a rich and creamy texture that make them easy to swipe on for a sheer to medium coverage.

--A kit of our buttery lip gloss with a sweet scent that provides sheer to medium coverage on your lips without that sticky feeling.
--Adore that it can be worn alone or over your favorite lipstick! 

They're delicious and gorgeous at the same time! 

Sugar Kisses, please be mine! 

--Apply on lips with the applicator included alone or over your favorite lipstick making your lips appear more voluptuous.

title: Revlon Just Bitten Kissing Balm Stain, Lovestick, 0.1 Ounce
description: Revlon Just bitten kissing balm stain provides a gorgeous flush of color and the moisturizing comfort of a balm in a portable, self sharpening chubby crayon.

title: 100 Multi Color 5mm Silicone Lined Micro-ring Links Beads Linkies for I Stick Hair Extension Installation and Feathers
description: A thin layer of silicone coats the center of these microlinks giving them extra holding power and to eliminate slippage. For use with a small size threading wire or needle. Silicone lined micro links or beads are to be used with the i-tip extensions.
